title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“How to protect your neighborhood against crime and Jennifer Beals, star of 'The Bride.' Live at Five.” [From a tease on CBS-TV (New York), 11 August 1985. Submitted by Robert Sherman Corwin, New York City.]
